課程概述 Course Description
       1. 認識重要的礦物陶瓷材料，包含其名稱及化學式2. 藉晶體模型的構築實習，來熟悉重要礦物陶瓷材料的結晶構造3. 學習結晶化學的基本概念4. 暸解晶體結構與物理性質的關連性 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	          1. 認識重要的礦物陶瓷材料，包含其名稱及化學式
      2. 藉晶體模型的構築實習，來熟悉重要礦物陶瓷材料的結晶構造
      3. 學習結晶化學的基本概念
      4. 暸解晶體結構與物理性質的關連性    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Outline and Chemical Elements2Minerals and Ceramic Raw Materials, Chemical Bonding in Ceramic Materials, Electronegativity3Hardness, Melting Points and Boiling Points, and Structure, Crystal Systems, Theoretical Density4Miller Indices and Zone Axes, Morphology and Crystal Growth5Mechanical Properties: Cleavage and Slip, Surface Properties: Wetting and Etching6Symmetry Elements and Point Groups, Neumann’s Law and Tensor Properties7Bond Lengths and Atomic Radii, Ionic Radii: Trends and Regularities8Pauling’s Rules for Ionic Structures, Prediction of Structures for Crystals and Glasses, Zachariasen’s Rules and Structure of Glass9期中考試10 Clays and Other Layer Silicates, Phase Diagrams and Crystal Chemistry11Types of Solid Solutions, Phase Transformations and Structure12Structure Changes with Temperature and Pressure, Thermal Expansion and Structure13Specific Heat, Thermal Conductivity, and Structure, Specific Heat, Thermal Conductivity, and Structure14Refractive Index and Birefringence, Color, Absorption, Fluorescence, and Structure15Dielectrics and Ferroelectricity16Magnetism and Structure17Elasticity and Structure18期末考試 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


